        <num>4402</num>
        <heading>Motion for continuance or new trial during trial</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  Rule 4402. Motion for continuance or new trial during trial. At any\ntime during the trial, the court, on motion of any party, may order a\ncontinuance or a new trial in the interest of justice on such terms as\nmay be just.\n</p>
